{"title":"伊甸园蛇的愤懑","authors":["林林"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":2,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊甸园蛇的愤懑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来长得也很好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不料挨受了重刑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被削掉能飞的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这么肚皮贴地爬行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又折磨了亚当夏娃伉俪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也无法将这严令变更。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有用假话骗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说的全是有根有据。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那美好的智慧果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生在善恶树的树枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何再三下禁令？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准摸、不准吃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若从亚当夏娃那时起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们那么眼不亮心不明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真假不能辨识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善恶不能分清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那人类算什么世界？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊甸园怎能是仙境？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"智慧果由上帝独占，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要别人愚昧盲从。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶残滥用权力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随意指使天兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我招认确把天机泄漏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让公众看穿至尊的品性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八九年二月四日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}